description: BMO BBB Corporate Bond Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the FTSE Canada 1-10 Year BBB Corporate Bond Index, net of expenses. The Fund invests in debt securities with a term to maturity greater than one year and less than ten years. Securities held in the Index are corporate bonds issued domestically in Canada in Canadian dollars, with a BBB rating.
name: BMO BBB Corporate Bond Index ETF
